AniCrave Entity Relationship Diagram (ERD)
This document outlines the data model for the AniCrave website, based on the current 
db.json
 schema and implied relationships.

Overview
The application consists of three main entities:

Users: Registered accounts on the platform.
Anime: The catalog of anime titles available.
Favorites: A relationship linking Users to their preferred Anime.
